2005年2月11日，捷克下議院82人贊成、65人反對、18人棄權否決同性伴侶關係權利法案。12月16日，捷克下議院86人贊成、54人反對、7人棄權通過同性伴侶關係權利法案<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.radio.cz/en/article/73886 |title=Czech MPs approve law on same-sex partnerships |access-date=2011-07-02 |archive-date=2009-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090705185231/http://www.radio.cz/en/article/73886 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.gaydaradio.co.uk/UserPortal/Article/Detail.aspx?ID=17848&sid=5 Czech Republic Takes First Step Towards Legal Gay Marriage]{{Dead link|date=2019年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20051218050518/http://365gay.com/Newscon05/12/121605czech.htm Czech Republic, Austria Move To Legalize Gay Unions]</ref>。2006年1月25日，捷克上議院以45票贊成、14票反對和6票缺席通過同性伴侶關係登記與權利法案。2月16日，捷克總統克勞斯否決同性伴侶關係登記與權利法案。3月15日，捷克下議院以101票贊成（議員總數為200人，本次有效票數為177票）推翻了總統對同性伴侶關係權利法案的否決，成為第一個法律認可同性伴侶關係的歐洲前社會主義國家。7月1日，捷克同性伴侶關係法案生效。

==同性婚姻==
[[綠黨_(捷克)|綠黨]]和[[捷克海盜黨|海盜黨]]在2017年的選舉過程中表示支持[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Manželství pro všechny|url=https://www.zeleni.cz/lgbt/|work=zeleni.cz|access-date=2020-04-12|archive-date=2019-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190525051520/https://www.zeleni.cz/lgbt/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Nová Sněmovna má 82 férových poslanců|url=http://www.jsmefer.cz/vse_o_nove_snemovne|work=Jsme Fér|access-date=2020-04-12|archive-date=2019-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190321081155/https://www.jsmefer.cz/vse_o_nove_snemovne|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[总理|總理]][[安德烈·巴比什|安德烈·巴比斯]]支持同性婚姻合法化。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Babiš podpořil sňatky homosexuálů|url=https://www.novinky.cz/domaci/501885-babis-podporil-snatky-homosexualu.html|date=7 April 2019|work=Novinky.cz|language=cs|access-date=2020-04-12|archive-date=2019-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190408202139/https://www.novinky.cz/domaci/501885-babis-podporil-snatky-homosexualu.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Czech prime minister supports marriage equality|url=https://www.ebar.com/news/news//274694|date=10 April 2019|work=The Bay Area Reporter|access-date=2020-04-12|archive-date=2019-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412203551/https://www.ebar.com/news/news//274694|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Czech Prime Minister Andrej Babiš voices support for gay marriage|url=https://news.expats.cz/weekly-czech-news/czech-prime-minister-andrej-babis-voices-support-for-gay-marriage/|date=9 April 2019|work=news.expats.cz|access-date=2020-04-12|archive-date=2019-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412203715/https://news.expats.cz/weekly-czech-news/czech-prime-minister-andrej-babis-voices-support-for-gay-marriage/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Andrej Babiš podpoří gay manželství. Diskutovat na toto téma bude v kině Varšava Zdroj|url=https://jablonecky.denik.cz/z-regionu/andrej-babis-podpori-gay-manzelstvi-diskutovat-na-toto-tema-bude-v-kine-varsava-20170419.html|date=19 April 2017|work=deník.cz|language=cs|access-date=2020-04-12|archive-date=2019-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190710124214/https://jablonecky.denik.cz/z-regionu/andrej-babis-podpori-gay-manzelstvi-diskutovat-na-toto-tema-bude-v-kine-varsava-20170419.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年6月12日，46名[[捷克众议院|眾議院]]代表提出了同性婚姻法案<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.psp.cz/sqw/historie.sqw?o=8&T=201|title=Sněmovní tisk 201 - Novela z. - občanský zákoník|accessdate=15 June 2018|publisher=Chamber of Deputies of the Czech Republic|work=psp.cz|date=12 June 2018|archive-date=2019-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190429010943/http://www.psp.cz/sqw/historie.sqw?o=8&T=201|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.lidovky.cz/dustojnost-pro-vsechny-poslanci-navrhli-aby-manzelstvi-mohli-uzavirat-i-lide-stejneho-pohlavi-i2d-/zpravy-domov.aspx?c=A180613_161954_ln_domov_ele|title="Důstojnost pro všechny". Poslanci navrhli, aby manželství mohli uzavírat i lidé stejného pohlaví|trans-title="Dignity for all": Legislators suggest that marriage be opened to same-sex couples.|accessdate=14 June 2018|date=13 June 2018|website=lidovky.cz|archive-date=2018-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180614021211/https://www.lidovky.cz/dustojnost-pro-vsechny-poslanci-navrhli-aby-manzelstvi-mohli-uzavirat-i-lide-stejneho-pohlavi-i2d-/zpravy-domov.aspx?c=A180613_161954_ln_domov_ele|dead-url=no}}</ref>。三天後，另外37名代表提出限定婚姻為一男一女結合的憲法修正案，以作為回應。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sněmovní tisk 211 - N. ústav. z. - Listina základních práv a svobod|url=http://www.psp.cz/sqw/historie.sqw?o=8&T=211|date=13 June 2018|work=psp.cz|access-date=2020-04-12|archive-date=2019-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190321081148/http://www.psp.cz/sqw/historie.sqw?o=8&T=211|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Skupina poslanců odmítá sňatky pro homosexuály. Svazek muže a ženy chce chránit ústavně|url=http://www.ceskatelevize.cz/ct24/domaci/2511124-skupina-poslancu-odmita-snatky-pro-homosexualy-svazek-muze-a-zeny-chce-chranit|date=13 June 2018|work=Ceska Televize|access-date=2020-04-12|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622164851/http://www.ceskatelevize.cz/ct24/domaci/2511124-skupina-poslancu-odmita-snatky-pro-homosexualy-svazek-muze-a-zeny-chce-chranit|dead-url=no}}</ref> 同性婚姻法案需要在眾議院通過簡單多數決，而修憲案則要求120票。6月22日， 巴比斯政府宣布支持同性婚姻法案。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Manželství místo partnerství. Vláda podpořila sňatky pro homosexuályl|url=https://www.denik.cz/z_domova/manzelstvi-misto-partnerstvi-vlada-podporila-navrh-na-snatky-pro-homosexualy-20180622.html|date=22 June 2018|work=denik.cz|access-date=2020-04-12|archive-date=2018-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180709225945/https://www.denik.cz/z_domova/manzelstvi-misto-partnerstvi-vlada-podporila-navrh-na-snatky-pro-homosexualy-20180622.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Manželství budou moci podle Babišovy vlády uzavřít i homosexuálové|url=https://zpravy.idnes.cz/manzelstvi-homosexualove-vlada-registrovane-partnerstvi-pax-/domaci.aspx?c=A180622_105327_domaci_kop|date=22 June 2018|work=zpravy.idnes.cz|access-date=2020-04-12|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622140315/https://zpravy.idnes.cz/manzelstvi-homosexualove-vlada-registrovane-partnerstvi-pax-/domaci.aspx?c=A180622_105327_domaci_kop|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Czech government backs bill on same-sex marriage|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-czech-marriage/czech-government-backs-bill-on-same-sex-marriage-idUSKBN1JI1H6|date=22 June 2018|work=Reuters|access-date=2020-04-12|archive-date=2018-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180704190554/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-czech-marriage/czech-government-backs-bill-on-same-sex-marriage-idUSKBN1JI1H6|dead-url=no}}</ref> 「我們公平(We are fair)」運動在6月下旬向眾議院提出了70,350個支持同性婚姻法案的連署。<ref name="praguemonitor">{{Cite web|title=Petition for same-sex marriage passed to lawmakers|url=http://www.praguemonitor.com/2018/06/27/petition-same-sex-marriage-passed-lawmakers|date=27 June 2018|work=Prague Monitor|access-date=2020-04-12|archive-date=2019-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190321081154/http://www.praguemonitor.com/2018/06/27/petition-same-sex-marriage-passed-lawmakers|dead-url=no}}</ref> 該法案的一讀原定於10月31日，但被延遲到11月14日。<ref>{{Cite web|title=První čtení: manželství pro všechny ve Sněmovně|url=https://www.jsmefer.cz/prvni_cteni|date=31 October 2018|work=Jsme fér|language=cs|access-date=2020-04-12|archive-date=2019-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190321081146/https://www.jsmefer.cz/prvni_cteni|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Czech Republic fails to vote on same-sex marriage, puts it off for later session|url=https://www.gaystarnews.com/article/czech-republic-fails-vote-same-sex-marriage/|author=Crittenton|date=31 October 2018|first=Anya|work=Gay Star News|access-date=2020-04-12|archive-date=2019-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190416193952/https://www.gaystarnews.com/article/czech-republic-fails-vote-same-sex-marriage/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 自兩案開始辯論以來，各國會議員是針對該議題的正反立場發言，不是依據政黨分別，而是進行{{link-en|良知投票|conscience vote}}。<ref>{{Cite web|title=CZECH MPS DEBATE SAME-SEX MARRIAGE, VOTE POSSIBLE IN JANUARY|url=https://www.radio.cz/en/section/news/czech-mps-debate-same-sex-marriage-vote-possible-in-january|accessdate=20 December 2018|author=Kenety|first=Brian|work=Radio Praha|archive-date=2019-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190321081148/https://www.radio.cz/en/section/news/czech-mps-debate-same-sex-marriage-vote-possible-in-january|dead-url=no}}</ref> 原定2019年1月將再次進行表決，但後來推遲到2019年3月26日；<ref>{{Cite web|title=Guess who’s coming to dinner? LGBTQ couple could win Christian Democrats’ marriage contest {{!}} Radio Prague|url=http://www.radio.cz/en/section/curraffrs/guess-whos-coming-to-dinner-lgbtq-couple-could-win-christian-democrats-marriage-contest|accessdate=2019-02-27|work=Radio Praha|language=en|archive-date=2019-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190321081155/https://www.radio.cz/en/section/curraffrs/guess-whos-coming-to-dinner-lgbtq-couple-could-win-christian-democrats-marriage-contest|dead-url=no}}</ref> 然而，當日並未進行表決，且亦未宣布新的表決日期。

